### Logo & Visual Assets

**Logo Specifications:**
- **Primary Logo:** Combination mark featuring:
  - Icon: Stylized green leaf emerging from soil/smartphone fusion
  - Wordmark: "Krishi Mitra" in Devanagari (कृषि मित्र) and English
  - Government of Punjab emblem on official versions

- **Logo Variations:**
  - Full color on white background (primary)
  - White on green background (app header)
  - Icon-only for app launcher (512x512px)
  - Monochrome for official documents

- **Safe Space:** Minimum clear space equal to height of leaf icon
- **Minimum Size:** 120px width for full logo, 48px for icon-only
- **File Formats:** SVG (web/vector), PNG (raster exports), ICO (app icon)

**Imagery Style:**
- **Photography:** Authentic Indian agricultural scenes - real farmers, crops, fields; warm natural lighting; focus on hands, soil, and crops
- **Illustrations:** Flat, friendly, iconic style with bold outlines; representing farming activities, weather, crops; culturally relevant (dhoti-kurta, sarees, turbans)
- **Icons:** Google Material Symbols (Rounded variant) for universal recognition; supplemented with custom agriculture icons
- **Patterns/Textures:** Subtle grain/seed patterns for backgrounds; never overwhelming; earth tones

