| **User** | account, account-group, logout, settings | Profile, community |
| **Pest/Disease** | bug, virus, shield-check, medical-bag | Disease detection, treatment |
| **Status** | check-circle, alert, weather-lightning, star | Crop health, alerts, ratings |

**Icon Sizes:**

- Small: 20px (inline with text, tags)
- Medium: 28px (list items, cards)
- Large: 40px (primary actions, feature cards)
- XL: 64px (onboarding, empty states)

**Icon Component:**

```tsx
import Icon from 'react-native-vector-icons/MaterialCommunityIcons';

interface IconProps {
  name: string;
  size?: number;
  color?: string;
  onPress?: () => void;
}

const CustomIcon: FC<IconProps> = ({
  name,
  size = 24,
  color = theme.colors.onSurface,
  onPress
}) => {
  return (
    <Icon
      name={name}
      size={size}
      color={color}
      onPress={onPress}
      accessible={true}
      accessibilityRole="imagebutton"
    />
  );
};
```

