### Responsive Design (Mobile-First)

**Device Support:**

```tsx
const deviceSizes = {
  small: 320,   // Small budget phones (Galaxy J2, Redmi 4A)
  medium: 360,  // Standard phones (most Android devices)
  large: 400,   // Larger phones (OnePlus, Samsung flagships)
  tablet: 600,  // Small tablets (future consideration)
};
```

**Layout Patterns:**

**All Screens (Mobile-Only MVP):**

- Single-column layout (no multi-column for simplicity)
- Full-width cards with 16px horizontal padding
- Large touch targets (minimum 56px height for buttons)
- Bottom navigation bar (always visible)
- Sticky headers for context retention

**Component Sizing:**

```tsx
/* Primary Buttons */
<Button style={{ height: 56, width: '100%' }}>
  Large, Easy-to-Tap
</Button>

/* Cards */
<Card style={{ marginHorizontal: 16, marginVertical: 8, borderRadius: 12 }}>
  Content with generous padding
</Card>

/* Bottom Navigation */
<NavigationBar style={{ height: 72 }}>
  Icons + Labels (always visible)
</NavigationBar>
```

**Screen Adaptations:**

**Small Phones (320px-359px):**
- Slightly reduced font sizes (-2px)
- Single-column grid (1 card per row)
- Compact spacing (12px instead of 16px)

**Medium Phones (360px-399px):**
- Standard sizing (base design)
- Comfortable spacing (16px)
- 2-column grid for weather cards only

**Large Phones (400px+):**
- Enhanced spacing (20px)
- Slightly larger headings (+2px)
- 2-column layout for advisory cards

---

### Accessibility Requirements

**WCAG 2.1 AA Compliance + Rural Context:**

**Perceivable:**

- [x] All images have descriptive alt text (in current language)
- [x] Color contrast ratio ≥ 7:1 for all text (AAA level for outdoor visibility)
- [x] Icons ALWAYS paired with text labels
- [x] Weather/status information uses icons + text + color
- [x] Text size minimum 16px (outdoor readability)
- [x] High contrast mode available

**Operable:**

- [x] All functionality available via touch (no